UR  - https://doi.org/10.1111/0022-1082.00048
Y2  - 2024/03/26
N2  - ABSTRACT This paper develops static hedges for several exotic options using standard options. The method relies on a relationship between European puts and calls with different strike prices. The analysis allows for constant volatility or for volatility smiles or frowns.
ER  - 

